cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV

This paper proposes a method for improving exploration in policy gradient methods, which are commonly used in reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also includes experiments on image-based tasks, which suggests a possible connection to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the use of conjugate gradient descent suggests a possible connection to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
